}}</ref>}}

==Pitching Style==
Brackman consistently throws his [[fastball]] between 92-97 miles per hour, and he compliments it with a [[two-seam fastball]], [[knuckle curve]], and a [[changeup]].<ref>[http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/events/draft/y2007/drafttracker.jsp The Official Site of Major League Baseball: Events: 2007 DraftTracker<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

